{"tid":1107800,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[娛樂台已死]難以置信，BLACKPINK上COACHELLA表演竟然冇人講","createTime":"2019-04-15T13:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T14:19:27.000Z","uid":58335,"like":11,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"040e47bf48fc860ad71432d5f3994a7e1b25a5ff","tid":1107800,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"BLACKPINK上COACHELLA呢D大型表演<br />\n娛樂台竟然冇人講<img src=\"https://news.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default/smile_42.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.discuss.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_42.gif&h=e55a0b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不得不說娛樂台已死<img src=\"https://news.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default/smile_39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.discuss.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_39.gif&h=dc517a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我BP果然世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK參與美國音樂節引轟動 Lisa被瘋狂搜尋：個瀏海妹好正<br />\n韓國女團BLACKPINK新專輯《Kill This Love》音源於4月5日面世，四位成員Jisoo、Jennie、Ros&eacute;與Lisa近日在韓國、泰國、美國等地宣傳新專輯同名新歌《Kill This Love》，BLACKPINK更獲世界級音樂盛典「Coachella」邀請，與Ariana Grande、Billie Elish、Dennis Lloyd、H.E.R.、Jaden Smith、Staroz、還有同樣來自韓國的Hyukoh和Jambinai等音樂人參與演出，成為首隊登上「Coachella」舞台的韓國女團。<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK的表演長達一小時，先後獻唱《DDU-DU DDU-DU》、《Stay》、《Whistle》、《Kill This Love》、《Playing with Fire》、《Boombayah》、《As If It's Your Last》等歌曲，Jennie亦有獻唱個人單曲《Solo》。BLACKPINK的表演不只獲Billboard、BBC、MTV、Metro等媒體報道，更造成Twitter轟動，網民尤其對瀏海馬尾的Lisa大感興趣，紛紛在網上搜尋「Coachella瀏海女孩」（Girl with bangs in Coachella），又表示「雖然我不是BLACKPINK歌迷，不過瀏海女孩真的不得了！可以告訴我她是誰嗎？」、「BLACKPINK那個叫Lisa的女孩極有魅力」、<span style=\"color: red;\">「沒有惡意，不過我想BLACKPINK的Lisa踩在我身上！</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可見今次表演令Lisa收獲大批粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/317788/blackpink%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E7%AF%80%E5%BC%95%E8%BD%9F%E5%8B%95-lisa%E8%A2%AB%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82%E6%90%9C%E5%B0%8B-%E5%80%8B%E7%80%8F%E6%B5%B7%E5%A6%B9%E5%A5%BD%E6%AD%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F317788%2Fblackpink%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E7%25AF%2580%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BD%259F%25E5%258B%2595-lisa%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2598%258B%25E7%258B%2582%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%25B0%258B-%25E5%2580%258B%25E7%2580%258F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%25AD%25A3&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUamrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=c77f62dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/317788/blackpink%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E7%AF%80%E5%BC%95%E8%BD%9F%E5%8B%95-lisa%E8%A2%AB%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82%E6%90%9C%E5%B0%8B-%E5%80%8B%E7%80%8F%E6%B5%B7%E5%A6%B9%E5%A5%BD%E6%AD%A3</a>"},{"pid":"14436ecbf661f2591c1ba1628f95f7bb62c58e58","tid":1107800,"uid":33359,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"7c66591211896c7ced7449a23957456e5d18bc38","tid":1107800,"uid":58335,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:28:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yhgs6PxJCwI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dyhgs6PxJCwI&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUamrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=d124d92c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yhgs6PxJCwI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mBkqHWMt2U4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmBkqHWMt2U4&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUamrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=6ae89603\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mBkqH